item.title: You Won't Believe What Happened When This Person Tried to Make a Paper Airplane World Record!
item.description: You Won’t Believe What Happened When This Person Tried to Make a Paper Airplane World Record! We’ve all tried to make paper airplanes at some point in our lives, but have you ever tried to make one that could break a world record? One person recently attempted to do just that, and the results were shocking! Introduction This is the story of one person’s attempt to break the world record for longest flight time for a paper airplane.
